任务三演算过程: [骰#9 等级: (${tasks[2].rolls.difficulty}) -> (${tasks[2].difficulty})], [骰#10 类型: (${tasks[2].rolls.type}) -> (${tasks[2].type})], [骰#11 种族: (${tasks[2].rolls.race1}) -> (${tasks[2].race1})], [骰#12 种族: (${tasks[2].rolls.race2}) -> (${tasks[2].race2})]
宿敌演算过程: [最高任务难度: ${maxTaskDifficultyStr} >= B? ${isRivalCheckTriggered ? '是' : '否'}], [骰#13 宿敌: (${rivalRoll}) -> (${rivalResult})]
-->`;
